🔁 3. Entry Lifecycle (this is critical)

Step 1: Capture

User interacts → system proposes Entry

Step 2: Structure

Auto-fill:
	•	summary
	•	mechanism
	•	use cases

User edits

⸻

Step 3: Critique (mandatory)

System runs:
	•	what’s vague?
	•	what’s missing?
	•	what’s unproven?

⸻

Step 4: Promote or Sandbox
	•	sandbox → experimental
	•	active → usable in workflows
	•	canonical → reusable across system

⸻

Step 5: Reuse + Mutation

Entries:
	•	get reused in prompts
	•	evolve into variants
	•	gain confidence over time

